<p>Privacy Policy &mdash; MyInboxer.com<br /><br />Version:&nbsp;<br />Last Updated: 12/12/2025<br /><br />1. Overview<br />This Privacy Policy explains how MyInboxer.com processes, stores, and protects your personal data when you use our spam-recovery service.<br />We follow major data protection laws including GDPR, CPRA, and other global standards.<br /><br />2. Data We Collect<br />A. Information You Provide<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Account email address<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Authentication information (OAuth, tokens)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Profile preferences and settings<br />We do not collect your email password.<br /><br />B. Data Accessed Through Integrations<br />To identify and rescue misclassified emails, MyInboxer accesses:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Email metadata (sender, subject)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Spam/junk folder labels<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Message flags (read/unread, importance)<br /><br />We do not permanently store full email content unless required for troubleshooting and only with your explicit permission.<br />C. Automatically Collected Data<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Device/browser information<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Usage analytics<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; IP address (for security)<br /><br />3. How We Use Your Data<br />We use your data to:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Detect legitimate emails incorrectly marked as spam<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Improve spam detection algorithms<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Provide customer support<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Maintain platform security<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Fulfill legal obligations<br />We never sell your data or email content.<br /><br />4. Legal Bases (GDPR)<br />We process your data on:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Contractual necessity (to deliver the Service)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Legitimate interest (security, usage analytics)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Consent (cookie choices, optional features)<br /><br />5. Data Sharing<br />We only share data with:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Essential service providers (cloud hosting, payment processors)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Email provider APIs (Google, Microsoft, etc.)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Legal authorities when required by law<br />We never share or sell email data for advertising.<br /><br />6. Data Storage &amp; Retention<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Minimal email metadata is temporarily cached for filtering<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; We do not archive or store full emails<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Account data is deleted within 30&ndash;90 days after account deletion<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Backups follow a secure rotation schedule<br /><br />7. Security Measures<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; End-to-end encryption in transit<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Encrypted storage at rest<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Strict access controls<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; OAuth-based secure permissions<br /><br />8. Your Rights<br />Depending on your region, you may request:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Access to your data<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Correction or deletion<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Restriction of processing<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Export of your data (portability)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Withdrawal of consent<br />Contact: privacy@myinboxer.com<br /><br />9. International Transfers<br />Data may be processed globally, always under standard contractual clauses (SCCs) and strict protection measures.<br /><br />10. Changes<br />We may update this Privacy Policy periodically.</p>
